    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Sanskrit term Sukham has multiple  &lt;br&gt;
English translations like happiness, pleasure, joy, etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sukham is the experience of an individual.  &lt;br&gt;
It is your own internal feeling.  &lt;br&gt;
It is not an objective reality outside,  &lt;br&gt;
like any physical thing.  &lt;br&gt;
The objective reality outside has an influence on this feeling  &lt;br&gt;
but for a wise person, it is in his own control that how he wants to feel.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
